_sText:
Hey!

This is my second released GunGame Map.
It's called gg_Train_Fight because the Map is based on de_Train.
I tried to optimized the Map as much as possible.
It have High FPS(100-180) and it has a good Gameplay.
The Map is balanced and has 64 Spawnpoints.
I recommened to play this Map with up to 32 Players.

-Secret Spots and Ways
-Balanced
-Funny
-High Fps(100-180)
-64 Spawnpoints
-Detailed
